### RuntimeExecutions V2 API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 查询运行执行列表
# 响应字段包含 workflowId/runtimeContextId/releaseId/appId/errorCategory，便于发布闭环追溯
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询运行执行列表（多条件筛选）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&appId=1001&status=Failed&startedFrom=2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z&startedTo=2026-12-31T23:59:59.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 运行执行统计聚合（全量）
# 返回 total/running/succeeded/failed/cancelled/avgDurationMs/p95DurationMs/errorCategories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 运行执行统计聚合（按应用+时间范围）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions/stats?appId=1001&startedFrom=2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z&startedTo=2026-12-31T23:59:59.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询运行执行详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询运行执行审计轨迹
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions/1/audit-trails?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 取消执行
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 重试执行
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions/1/retry
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 恢复执行
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions/1/resume
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 单节点调试
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions/1/debug
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodeKey": "Start",
  "inputsJson": "{\"demo\":true}"
}

### 超时诊断
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions/1/timeout-diagnosis
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
